%META:TOPICPARENT{name="WebHome"}%
---+ Keyboard Shortcuts

%TOC%

All shortcuts are single-press, no modifier. Typing into a text field
(threshold input, search) suppresses the hotkeys until focus leaves.

---++ Camera

| *Key*      | *Action*                                        |
| Mouse drag | Orbit camera                                    |
| Scroll     | Zoom                                            |
| Right-drag | Pan                                             |
| =R=        | Reset view to the default isometric             |
| =1 / 2 / 3=| Top / side / isometric presets                  |

---++ Panels

| *Key*      | *Action*                                        |
| =M=        | Toggle the left (sidebar) panel                 |
| =E=        | Toggle the right (energy threshold) panel       |
| =G=        | Toggle the ATLAS Ghost panel                    |
| =S=        | Open the settings panel                         |
| =?=        | Open the shortcuts cheat-sheet (in Settings)    |
| =Esc=      | Close the topmost overlay / exit cinema         |

---++ Scene toggles

| *Key*      | *Action*                                        |
| =T=        | Toggle TILE sub-detector                        |
| =L= / =A=   | Toggle LAr                                     |
| =H=        | Toggle HEC                                      |
| =J=        | Toggle reconstructed tracks                     |
| =K=        | Toggle topological clusters                     |
| =Shift+K=  | Toggle the cluster-E_T threshold switch         |
| =I=        | Toggle cell-hover tooltip and outline           |
| =B=        | Toggle beam-axis indicator                      |
| =Shift+B=  | Open the scene-background colour picker         |
| =Shift+S=  | Toggle the spherical slicer bubble              |
| =C=        | Cinema mode — hide UI, auto-rotate or tour      |

---++ Data source

| *Key*      | *Action*                                        |
| =← / →=     | Previous / next event in the current list      |
| =Space=    | Pause / resume live polling                     |

---++ Output

| *Key*      | *Action*                                        |
| =P=        | Screenshot — open resolution picker             |
| =/=        | Focus the event-list search box                 |

See [[UserInterface][User Interface]] for the corresponding buttons and
panels.

